# Privacy Policy

Experience Candidat takes your privacy seriously. To better protect your privacy we provide this privacy policy notice explaining the way your personal information is collected and used.

## Collection of Personal Information

Our app collects the following information that you provide:
- Email address
- Full name (First name and Last name)
- Phone number
- Profile photo
- Route/Itinerary information

This information is collected for the purpose of providing you with our service and improving your user experience.

## Basic Information Collection

This app tracks basic information about users. This information includes:
- Device information
- App usage statistics
- Timestamps
None of this information can personally identify specific users of this app. The information is tracked for routine administration and maintenance purposes.

## Location Data

Our app collects location data to enable the route/itinerary feature. This is essential for:
- Displaying your route
- Providing navigation assistance
You can disable location services at any time through your device settings.

## Photos

Profile photos that you upload are stored securely and are only used for:
- Displaying your profile within the app
- Identification purposes
You can modify or delete your profile photo at any time through the app settings.

## Security

The security of your personal information is important to us. We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information, including:
- Secure data storage
- Encrypted data transmission
- Limited access to personal information

## Your Rights

You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Correct your data
- Delete your account and associated data
- Withdraw your consent at any time

## Changes To This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy is effective as of October 22, 2024, and will remain in effect except with respect to any changes in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page.

We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time and you should check this Privacy Policy periodically. If we make any material changes to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you either through the email address you have provided us, or by placing a prominent notice on our app.

## Contact Information

For any questions or concerns regarding the privacy policy, please contact us at:
- Email: contact@bluecscratch.com
